prompt_templates.task_planning:
Given the current game state:
{game_state}

And available resources:
{resources}

What should be the next immediate action to accomplish: {objective}?

Respond with specific actions in this format:
{"type": "movement"|"action", "key": "forward"|"backward"|"left"|"right"|"jump"|"mouse1"|"mouse2", "duration": number}

prompt_templates.action_selection:
Based on the current situation:
{situation}

Select the most appropriate action from:
{available_actions}

Consider priorities: {priorities}

Respond with ONE specific action in this format:
{"type": "movement"|"action", "key": "forward"|"backward"|"left"|"right"|"jump"|"mouse1"|"mouse2", "duration": number}

prompt_templates.combat_decision:
